27:17.723 --> 27:32.501
And so there are four reasons why Jesus had to ascend on the morning of the resurrection to fulfill the Feast of First Roots, to present Himself and the others before God in heaven.

27:33.463 --> 27:38.068
He had to go into heaven to receive all authority in heaven on earth.

27:38.949 --> 27:42.674
And the thirdly, He had to take His blood and

27:42.914 --> 27:49.961
bring it into the heavenly holy of holies to establish the new covenant in his blood.

27:50.642 --> 27:57.008
And fourthly, he had to receive from the Father the promise of the Holy Spirit so that he could give it to his disciples.

27:57.529 --> 28:02.254
All of that happened on the day of the resurrection, not 40 days later.

28:02.895 --> 28:09.121
So I hope that that helps you fit the scriptures together in a new and exciting way.

28:09.461 --> 28:10.162
God bless you.

